@{JLEFT}@{LINDENT 4}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}
@{PAR}@{B}Standard Programs and Utilities@{UB}@{LINE}

The mSQL distribution contains several programs and utilities to
allow you to use and manage your databases.  The tools provided
allow you to communicate with the database server, import data,
export data, submit queries and view your database structures.@{LINE}
@{FG TEXT}@{JLEFT}@{LINDENT 40}

